INSERT INTO contract_item
            (
                contract_id,
                is_included,
                is_blueprint_copy,

                quantity,

                record_id,
                type_id,
                item_id,

                material_efficiency,
                time_efficiency,
                runs
            )
            SELECT $1, * FROM UNNEST(
                $2::BOOLEAN[],
                $3::BOOLEAN[],
                $4::BIGINT[],
                $5::BIGINT[],
                $6::INTEGER[],
                $7::BIGINT[],
                $8::INTEGER[],
                $9::INTEGER[],
                $10::INTEGER[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (contract_id, record_id)
            DO NOTHING
